Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides Bowling Alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm calling about a billing issue I encountered. But first, could you tell me your company's operating hours?

Of course! Our operating hours are from nine zero zero AM to nine zero zero PM every day. May I have your name, please?

Yes, my name is Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Could you please tell me the billing issue you're experiencing?

Sure, I noticed that I was charged twice for my last visit to the bowling alley.

I'm sorry to hear that. To help you accurately, could I have the date of your visit and the exact amount billed?

I visited on the twelfth of August, and the amount billed was one hundred dollars.

Thank you for the details, Jamie. I'll look into this immediately and follow up with you soon.

Great, thank you for your help, Alex.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your patience and for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a wonderful day!
